window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The much-anticipated continuation of the Ash and Sand trilogy....&nbsp;</p> <p>Follow the long, bloody journey of Ruka, son of Beyla, through the islands of Pyu and the frozen wastes of the Ascom. See the return home of Ratama Kale Alaku, the \"Sorcerer-Prince\", and the terrifying rise of his \"miracles\". Before the end, a shocking history will unravel, ancient connections unfold, and all will learn the cost of unleashing the Kings of Ash....</p>"; 
